Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 迈步出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪是闪闪发光的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化为甘霖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的东西就舍去 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无限广阔的心中蔓延开来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于受伤时刻之外　看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若现在开始映入双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得强大 抓住机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想绝对能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遥远 都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感觉到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配了在遥远天空上的星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以第七界层为目标展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在身处的是有趣热带的第六星界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被魔法蜘蛛丝抓到的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在虎王跟玛达莉斯的帮助下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开了诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为此玛达莉斯失去了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四十三话\N海火子 哀伤的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里可以知道那家伙的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是热的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遥控
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑龙角修理好之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以让渡他们接近圣地亚索加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡还是个小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为你大意到现在为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被他们打败多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马哈路大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是由我亲自出动,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然罗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会要了渡的小命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他的灵魂交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我期待你,死亡遥控
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有守卫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然圣地就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看来不能轻易通过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遥控!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛达莉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟把玛达莉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把那家伙打倒的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们封锁他的魔术…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三人合力一口气…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那家伙绝对不能饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遥控!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要替玛达莉斯报仇!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些哆嗦我没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.00,0:05:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你由我来打倒!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲起来也没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎、火子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒语)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算把火美子怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的命已在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要用点力的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球粉碎了的话她便没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,用忍法啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用忍法从里面逃出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:12.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的声音是传不进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要她的命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用你的灵魂来交换
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用渡的灵魂?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢吞吞的话她便没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要袭击我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,渡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把灵魂给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王、海火子,我要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话,你的灵魂就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去引开他的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁这时候你们去救火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在过来!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你已死心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,放开火美子!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要等取你的灵魂之后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒语)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,跳进那里面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你的肉体就会变成灰只剩下灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒语)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想逃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把剑便会插进你的喉咙里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡是相信我们才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都会白费的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了,走吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会救你的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样打之不尽呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说这事的时候吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡的性命便要看我们了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王…海火子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡啊,到此为止了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快解开火美子的封印!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒语)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王、海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行,被他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑撒旦飞弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的对手已完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这大牛!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,小鬼…不能饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王那家伙自己去做饵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃得还真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是机会了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我是多坏达的人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是有什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话,能否告诉我?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我在找的男人会有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能找出他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变得很大件事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在找的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我丈夫为了打倒多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了第七界层
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是却被捉了变成了魔界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔界的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么,他现在在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和儿子在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丈夫被封印在儿子手上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…有这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某一天,只有那个球回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在里面的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是变成了魔界的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的儿子知不知道这事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:22.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子相信在球内的是他本来善良的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后为了救父亲开始了旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但请你制止我的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人复活了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星界山便完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你的儿子做傻事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子他很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好支持着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的力量只有这个程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么便由我开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(咒语)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯寒死光!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超龙雷拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,快逃呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行…动不了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了黑撒旦的厉害了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便是你的末日了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,什么家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也做你对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太嚣张呀,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶,阻碍者给我消失吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他打算干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒旦火炎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王…海火子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能动吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我便送你到黄泉!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,虎王起来呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡很危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去,龙星丸会被咬坏的!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把龙星丸的冰溶掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:15:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样溶掉呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且,再中多一次刚才那招的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也有危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是要那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃吧,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真顽强的小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的招式中多也不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话你现在便多尝一次那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你成功吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔猛虎飞弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王、海火子,谢谢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的实力不是说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么样做?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分别攻击不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三人合力务必对付了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,干吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这群小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一个不留的解决他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虎王、海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招,撒旦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.74,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变形,飞龙!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞龙光击拳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火子,我怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我终于集齐六颗珠了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏鬼丸变身了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:44.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火子的父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:19:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迟了一步吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难…难道那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸…爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多坏达大人兵众之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.26,0:20:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渔火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多坏达大人兵众?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于把我的封印解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的儿子海火子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记了爸爸了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的爸爸已和武一郎老师一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡遥控!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久没见了,死亡遥控
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶…饶恕我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是照命令把你封印而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打破自己的器皿的蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过…过分…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是岂有此理的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始把圣地亚索加的画完成
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使得暗黑龙复活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗…暗黑龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 阴霾的天空里乌云渐渐散去 阳光透过云层照了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.76,0:22:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人仰望这天空的哪个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眩目的彩虹 即将出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注定出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:23:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着光线还没有消失的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待着明天的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.22,0:23:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生辉的彩虹彼岸里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹出了两个人未来的风

